  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.14,
      "text": "Screen English"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.14,
      "end": 35.13,
      "text": "GMP 영화 배달 서비스 Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.13,
      "end": 38.13,
      "text": "10월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 After the Wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.13,
      "end": 39.75,
      "text": "After a Wedding in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.75,
      "end": 44.77,
      "text": "A movie starring Julian Moore, Michelle Williams, Billy Crudup, and Abby Quinn"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.77,
      "end": 45.27,
      "text": "Wow!"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.07,
      "end": 46.47,
      "text": "Hello!"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.77,
      "end": 47.49,
      "text": "잘 오셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.91,
      "end": 48.37,
      "text": "Good morning!"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.69,
      "end": 49.85,
      "text": "시작하기 전에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.85,
      "end": 52.37,
      "text": "Here's a GMPer who needs your advice."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.53,
      "end": 54.27,
      "text": "Oh, please ask me anything you want."
    },
    {
      "start": 54.35,
      "end": 55.85,
      "text": "너무 두근두근하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.93,
      "end": 56.37,
      "text": "Go ahead!"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.37,
      "end": 58.31,
      "text": "자, 78822님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.31,
      "end": 62.83,
      "text": "얼마 전에 외국인분이랑 잠깐 같이 자리할 일이 있었는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.29,
      "end": 65.49,
      "text": "무슨 말을 꺼내면 좋을지 모르겠더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.23,
      "end": 69.59,
      "text": "Small talk으로 할 만한 거 크리스 쌤이 알려주시면"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.59,
      "end": 72.53,
      "text": "다음에 한번 시도해 볼게요 하셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 72.59,
      "end": 73.35,
      "text": "Small talk!"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.75,
      "end": 76.13,
      "text": "그 놈의 small talk is very difficult."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.41,
      "end": 77.23,
      "text": "Do you have any idea?"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.49,
      "end": 79.45,
      "text": "It's difficult for native speakers too."
    },
    {
      "start": 79.61,
      "end": 83.63,
      "text": "But Americans are usually pretty good at small talk."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.77,
      "end": 84.89,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.89,
      "end": 86.63,
      "text": "If you don't know what to talk about,"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.09,
      "end": 89.41,
      "text": "there's always a few go-to subjects."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.57,
      "end": 89.87,
      "text": "뭐예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.47,
      "end": 90.87,
      "text": "Weather."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.11,
      "end": 92.19,
      "text": "아, 날씨."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.43,
      "end": 95.87,
      "text": "And then you talk about like an interest, sports."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.13,
      "end": 98.03,
      "text": "Many American guys like sports."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.65,
      "end": 101.57,
      "text": "But weather, it doesn't matter where you're from,"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.95,
      "end": 102.71,
      "text": "where you are."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.73,
      "end": 102.97,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.19,
      "end": 104.37,
      "text": "The weather is the same"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.37,
      "end": 106.61,
      "text": "because you're together under the same sky."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.01,
      "end": 108.99,
      "text": "우리나라 사람들도 마찬가지잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.61,
      "end": 110.95,
      "text": "괜히 좀 할 말 없으면"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.95,
      "end": 113.35,
      "text": "아, 오늘 날씨 참 쌀쌀하죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.35,
      "end": 116.23,
      "text": "아침에 좀, 날이 좀 추웠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.45,
      "end": 117.63,
      "text": "오늘 좀 더웠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.75,
      "end": 119.21,
      "text": "이런 말로 시작을 하잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.41,
      "end": 119.69,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.87,
      "end": 121.19,
      "text": "Or they talk about 환절기."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.33,
      "end": 121.55,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.67,
      "end": 122.13,
      "text": "환절기."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.33,
      "end": 122.97,
      "text": "조심하세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.05,
      "end": 123.75,
      "text": "감기 조심하세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.89,
      "end": 124.53,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.69,
      "end": 126.17,
      "text": "We don't say 환절기 though."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.79,
      "end": 128.79,
      "text": "Just 감기 조심하라는 말도 안 하고."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.33,
      "end": 131.27,
      "text": "Just, oh, the weather's cloudy today."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.43,
      "end": 133.11,
      "text": "Oh, it looks like it's going to rain."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.11,
      "end": 136.61,
      "text": "Oh, this weekend is supposed to be amazing weather."
    },
    {
      "start": 136.75,
      "end": 137.05,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.23,
      "end": 138.17,
      "text": "What are you going to do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.29,
      "end": 139.03,
      "text": "이런 거."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.17,
      "end": 142.69,
      "text": "Weather forecast까지 해나가면 되겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.83,
      "end": 144.17,
      "text": "Did you see the weather forecast?"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.47,
      "end": 146.77,
      "text": "It's going to be amazing this weekend."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.77,
      "end": 154.15,
      "text": "이야, 이와 같이 물 흐르듯이 인사처럼 이렇게 small talk 시작해내시면 충분히 좋을 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.41,
      "end": 155.53,
      "text": "Compliments are good too."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.65,
      "end": 157.39,
      "text": "Oh, hey, I like your necklace."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.73,
      "end": 161.45,
      "text": "아, 이렇게 칭찬으로 시작해주시면 더욱더 좋겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.55,
      "end": 162.07,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.21,
      "end": 163.69,
      "text": "Yeah, thanks for the advice."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.69,
      "end": 170.23,
      "text": "네, 78822님께서 아마 잘 숙지하시고 다음에 아주 훌륭한 small talk를 해내실 거라고 믿습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.35,
      "end": 172.05,
      "text": "Try it out and let us know how it went."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.25,
      "end": 173.71,
      "text": "Wow, 결과도 궁금하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.13,
      "end": 176.15,
      "text": "자, 이제 let's get straight to the point."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.39,
      "end": 177.19,
      "text": "Let's get started."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.43,
      "end": 184.43,
      "text": "Yeah, and this is a movie that makes us think about many choices we have to make throughout our lives."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.53,
      "end": 185.51,
      "text": "Big life choices."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.51,
      "end": 185.91,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.91,
      "end": 196.37,
      "text": "특히 이사벨의 경우를 보면, she had to decide whether or not to receive the huge amount of money from the person who's, you know, raised her daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.71,
      "end": 197.19,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.37,
      "end": 199.47,
      "text": "Oh, about 20 years?"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.05,
      "end": 200.99,
      "text": "20 years."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.03,
      "end": 201.29,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.39,
      "end": 202.05,
      "text": "Maybe more."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.35,
      "end": 203.75,
      "text": "Raised her own daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.89,
      "end": 204.97,
      "text": "Oh, for a long time."
    },
    {
      "start": 205.03,
      "end": 206.43,
      "text": "And wants to give her a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.67,
      "end": 207.07,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.49,
      "end": 208.07,
      "text": "I don't know why."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.13,
      "end": 209.21,
      "text": "I want that money, yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.21,
      "end": 211.51,
      "text": "It can help a lot of orphans in India."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.87,
      "end": 211.93,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.17,
      "end": 214.75,
      "text": "But I don't know if it comes with strings attached."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.75,
      "end": 216.63,
      "text": "So, she's in a predicament."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.77,
      "end": 217.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.25,
      "end": 223.99,
      "text": "이와 같이 선택을 앞두고 굉장히 갈등을 할 수 있을 법한 상황에 맞닥뜨리게 되었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.37,
      "end": 231.45,
      "text": "Also, Teresa, if you think about her side of the story, she has a disease that is incurable."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.93,
      "end": 240.79,
      "text": "So, she is going to pass away and she has to decide to give everything to this lady she just met for the first time."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.79,
      "end": 246.17,
      "text": "Her money, her family, her daughter, the girl she raised like a daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.37,
      "end": 248.81,
      "text": "So, it's not an easy decision for her either."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.81,
      "end": 249.09,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.83,
      "end": 251.71,
      "text": "저는 이 상황에서 이런 생각이 떠올라요."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.77,
      "end": 253.57,
      "text": "I can say, life is complex."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.09,
      "end": 254.39,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.53,
      "end": 255.71,
      "text": "Life is complicated."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.95,
      "end": 256.25,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.59,
      "end": 257.51,
      "text": "Sure, definitely."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.37,
      "end": 263.17,
      "text": "자, 이렇게 철학적인 생각을 하게 하는데 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.17,
      "end": 285.5,
      "text": "드디어 이 남편인 오스카가 found out that his wife was dying."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.06,
      "end": 286.36,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.36,
      "end": 290.8,
      "text": "He found her medicine hidden in her room."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.86,
      "end": 294.62,
      "text": "Oh, 특히 he found a medicine case in her drawer."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.74,
      "end": 295.92,
      "text": "And he called her doctor."
    },
    {
      "start": 296.08,
      "end": 296.56,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.26,
      "end": 310.74,
      "text": "특히 뭔가를 찾고 있는 장면에서 우연히 이 Teresa의 서랍을 열다가 거기에서 어떤 상자에 담겨서 있던 medicine case를 발견을 하고 주치의하고 통화를 하게 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 310.94,
      "end": 311.86,
      "text": "그러면서 알게 된 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.86,
      "end": 313.36,
      "text": "He got the shock of a lifetime."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.7,
      "end": 315.0,
      "text": "He's devastated, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 315.0,
      "end": 319.96,
      "text": "And she didn't want to change her family's life."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.18,
      "end": 322.28,
      "text": "So, she kept it a secret on purpose."
    },
    {
      "start": 322.48,
      "end": 326.2,
      "text": "She didn't want them to stop everything for her."
    },
    {
      "start": 326.86,
      "end": 328.24,
      "text": "So, I can understand that."
    },
    {
      "start": 328.44,
      "end": 329.9,
      "text": "But it's a tough choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.08,
      "end": 330.24,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.74,
      "end": 338.26,
      "text": "그래서 너무 당황을 해가지고 남편하고 이야기하다가 아주 황급히 자리를 떠나려는 모습도 보여줬었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.12,
      "end": 341.32,
      "text": "자, 중요 표현들 먼저 살펴볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.32,
      "end": 343.56,
      "text": "Experimental treatment."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.56,
      "end": 350.36,
      "text": "Experimental이라고 하면 실험 중인이라는 의미고, treatment 하면 치료가 되는 거잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.16,
      "end": 358.0,
      "text": "그럼 실험 중인 치료법 아니면 임상 실험 중인 치료법이라고도 해석을 할 수가 있겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 358.0,
      "end": 362.24,
      "text": "For her cancer, hopefully there's some kind of experimental treatment."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.6,
      "end": 363.84,
      "text": "That's what he's hoping."
    },
    {
      "start": 364.0,
      "end": 365.3,
      "text": "There isn't, but."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.5,
      "end": 369.74,
      "text": "Prolong it or make it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.48,
      "end": 374.98,
      "text": "Prolong이라는 단어 들으셨는데, P-R-O-L-O-N-G."
    },
    {
      "start": 375.48,
      "end": 376.1,
      "text": "Prolong."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.24,
      "end": 376.34,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.34,
      "end": 378.14,
      "text": "연장시키다."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.38,
      "end": 379.36,
      "text": "힌트 들으셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 379.52,
      "end": 380.04,
      "text": "Long."
    },
    {
      "start": 380.38,
      "end": 380.6,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.78,
      "end": 381.38,
      "text": "Not shorten."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.64,
      "end": 382.48,
      "text": "Prolong."
    },
    {
      "start": 383.14,
      "end": 383.9,
      "text": "연장시키다."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.0,
      "end": 384.82,
      "text": "라는 단어였어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.92,
      "end": 387.02,
      "text": "Prolong it or make it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.28,
      "end": 388.74,
      "text": "혹은 악화시키다."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.94,
      "end": 389.84,
      "text": "라는 의미가 되는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.68,
      "end": 391.78,
      "text": "We don't get to choose."
    },
    {
      "start": 391.78,
      "end": 393.76,
      "text": "우리에겐 선택권이 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 394.04,
      "end": 395.36,
      "text": "We don't get to choose."
    },
    {
      "start": 395.68,
      "end": 398.38,
      "text": "라는 문장도 통째로 기억해 두시면 되겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 399.06,
      "end": 400.2,
      "text": "이 내용 다시 한번 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.2,
      "end": 404.26,
      "text": "There's got to be some kind of experimental treatment or testing."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.54,
      "end": 404.88,
      "text": "There's not."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.98,
      "end": 405.4,
      "text": "I've looked."
    },
    {
      "start": 405.48,
      "end": 406.02,
      "text": "There's nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 406.1,
      "end": 408.92,
      "text": "There's nothing that wouldn't just prolong it or make it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 409.34,
      "end": 410.88,
      "text": "And I don't want you to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 410.96,
      "end": 412.54,
      "text": "And I don't want them to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.94,
      "end": 413.94,
      "text": "So you just want me to do nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.34,
      "end": 415.24,
      "text": "We don't get to choose."
    },
    {
      "start": 415.72,
      "end": 416.04,
      "text": "Let me go."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.1,
      "end": 419.22,
      "text": "It must be desperate enough."
    },
    {
      "start": 419.64,
      "end": 419.9,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.9,
      "end": 422.14,
      "text": "To both of them, for sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 422.28,
      "end": 422.88,
      "text": "They're both desperate."
    },
    {
      "start": 423.14,
      "end": 425.76,
      "text": "The situation is very desperate situation."
    },
    {
      "start": 426.76,
      "end": 428.44,
      "text": "자, 오스카가 먼저 이야기합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 429.53,
      "end": 433.05,
      "text": "There's got to be some kind of experimental treatment or testing."
    },
    {
      "start": 433.25,
      "end": 435.73,
      "text": "네, 여기에서 이제 말을 끊고"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.73,
      "end": 437.43,
      "text": "테레사가 들어오게 되는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 437.93,
      "end": 440.39,
      "text": "일단 오스카가 이야기했던 부분 해석해드리면"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.39,
      "end": 444.97,
      "text": "There's got to be some kind of experimental treatment or testing."
    },
    {
      "start": 445.19,
      "end": 445.71,
      "text": "점점점."
    },
    {
      "start": 445.81,
      "end": 446.73,
      "text": "There's got to be."
    },
    {
      "start": 446.85,
      "end": 448.51,
      "text": "He's holding on to hope."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.51,
      "end": 452.65,
      "text": "뭔가 희망사항으로 이야기하고 있는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 452.83,
      "end": 453.75,
      "text": "분명히 있을 거야."
    },
    {
      "start": 454.37,
      "end": 457.25,
      "text": "임상실험 중인 치료법이나 어떤 테스팅,"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.65,
      "end": 460.31,
      "text": "뭔가 테스트하고 있는 약물이 있을 거야."
    },
    {
      "start": 461.21,
      "end": 461.87,
      "text": "There's not."
    },
    {
      "start": 462.37,
      "end": 463.93,
      "text": "테레사가 대답한 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.17,
      "end": 464.57,
      "text": "없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.11,
      "end": 465.73,
      "text": "There's not."
    },
    {
      "start": 466.29,
      "end": 466.85,
      "text": "없다고."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.55,
      "end": 468.19,
      "text": "I've looked."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.45,
      "end": 469.07,
      "text": "There's nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.41,
      "end": 470.73,
      "text": "내가 이미 다 찾아봤는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.73,
      "end": 471.79,
      "text": "There's nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.01,
      "end": 472.75,
      "text": "아무것도 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.75,
      "end": 477.13,
      "text": "There's nothing that wouldn't just prolong it or make it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.13,
      "end": 482.81,
      "text": "진행을 늦추거나 악화시키거나 둘 중 하나야."
    },
    {
      "start": 482.99,
      "end": 483.75,
      "text": "아무것도 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.55,
      "end": 486.99,
      "text": "And I don't want you to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.33,
      "end": 490.13,
      "text": "그리고 I don't want you to see me 라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.13,
      "end": 493.13,
      "text": "당신이 나를 그렇게 보는 거 싫어 라는 의미였어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 493.45,
      "end": 495.85,
      "text": "I don't want you to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.85,
      "end": 500.61,
      "text": "And I don't want them to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.71,
      "end": 503.95,
      "text": "여기서 them이라는 것은 children 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.95,
      "end": 506.95,
      "text": "이제 Grace를 포함한 자녀들을 이야기하겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.07,
      "end": 507.61,
      "text": "Her kids."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.79,
      "end": 508.41,
      "text": "Her family."
    },
    {
      "start": 508.95,
      "end": 511.11,
      "text": "I don't want them to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 511.23,
      "end": 514.85,
      "text": "그리고 아이들한테도 나 그렇게 모습 보이기 싫어."
    },
    {
      "start": 515.75,
      "end": 517.81,
      "text": "So you just want me to do nothing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.19,
      "end": 519.71,
      "text": "오스카의 대답이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 519.71,
      "end": 522.05,
      "text": "So you just want me to do nothing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.53,
      "end": 525.63,
      "text": "그럼 나보고 아무것도 하지 말라는 얘기야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 525.97,
      "end": 526.89,
      "text": "This is difficult."
    },
    {
      "start": 527.37,
      "end": 529.79,
      "text": "He wants to fix, he wants to solve the problem."
    },
    {
      "start": 529.91,
      "end": 530.35,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 530.57,
      "end": 532.13,
      "text": "But there's no solution."
    },
    {
      "start": 532.49,
      "end": 535.01,
      "text": "아내가 incurable disease에 걸렸는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.01,
      "end": 537.05,
      "text": "남편의 입장에서 아무것도 할 수 없는"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.05,
      "end": 539.77,
      "text": "정말 좌절스러운 상황일 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 539.77,
      "end": 542.07,
      "text": "I mean even with something small"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.07,
      "end": 543.75,
      "text": "like the toilet is broken."
    },
    {
      "start": 543.97,
      "end": 547.03,
      "text": "I want to fix it but I can't."
    },
    {
      "start": 547.59,
      "end": 548.15,
      "text": "What's going to happen?"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.17,
      "end": 549.39,
      "text": "Have you ever experienced that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.77,
      "end": 550.95,
      "text": "I have several times."
    },
    {
      "start": 551.05,
      "end": 551.29,
      "text": "아 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.45,
      "end": 552.11,
      "text": "그냥 냅둬."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.25,
      "end": 553.07,
      "text": "Leave it alone."
    },
    {
      "start": 553.35,
      "end": 554.29,
      "text": "I'll do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.41,
      "end": 554.63,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 555.09,
      "end": 556.05,
      "text": "전문가가 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.23,
      "end": 556.41,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.69,
      "end": 558.05,
      "text": "There are 전문가s."
    },
    {
      "start": 558.35,
      "end": 559.49,
      "text": "And my wife is pretty good too."
    },
    {
      "start": 559.63,
      "end": 560.05,
      "text": "Oh really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 560.15,
      "end": 560.79,
      "text": "She's better."
    },
    {
      "start": 560.87,
      "end": 562.97,
      "text": "She's more handy around the house than I am."
    },
    {
      "start": 563.17,
      "end": 564.31,
      "text": "I didn't expect that."
    },
    {
      "start": 564.37,
      "end": 566.47,
      "text": "She thinks American guys are all handymen."
    },
    {
      "start": 566.67,
      "end": 567.63,
      "text": "It's not true."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.91,
      "end": 569.67,
      "text": "Only some of them are handymen."
    },
    {
      "start": 569.77,
      "end": 570.75,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 571.17,
      "end": 572.81,
      "text": "So you just want me to do nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.98,
      "end": 575.14,
      "text": "We don't get to choose."
    },
    {
      "start": 575.82,
      "end": 576.5,
      "text": "Let me go."
    },
    {
      "start": 576.7,
      "end": 578.24,
      "text": "Teresa가 이렇게 이야기한 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 578.34,
      "end": 579.54,
      "text": "We don't get to choose."
    },
    {
      "start": 579.96,
      "end": 581.22,
      "text": "우리는 선택권이 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 581.68,
      "end": 582.34,
      "text": "Let me go."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.7,
      "end": 585.3,
      "text": "자 여기에서 나 가게 냅도라는 말이었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.3,
      "end": 589.02,
      "text": "지금 차를 타고 가려고 이런 이야기를 한 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.12,
      "end": 589.58,
      "text": "Let me go."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.84,
      "end": 591.9,
      "text": "나 가게 좀 비켜라는 의도로"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.9,
      "end": 593.26,
      "text": "Let me go 라고 한 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.4,
      "end": 594.68,
      "text": "Oh she's a little irritated."
    },
    {
      "start": 594.9,
      "end": 595.12,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.56,
      "end": 596.16,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 596.16,
      "end": 598.56,
      "text": "이 장면을 제가 보면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.56,
      "end": 602.94,
      "text": "테리사가 must have had a hard time for a long time."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.24,
      "end": 603.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.64,
      "end": 606.78,
      "text": "Imagine hiding all that from your own family."
    },
    {
      "start": 606.86,
      "end": 607.24,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.28,
      "end": 609.24,
      "text": "The stress, the pressure, the emotion."
    },
    {
      "start": 610.12,
      "end": 610.3,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 610.38,
      "end": 613.66,
      "text": "Now it's all come out and the emotions are exploding."
    },
    {
      "start": 613.66,
      "end": 614.66,
      "text": "음 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.98,
      "end": 616.66,
      "text": "이 장면 한 번 더 확인해 보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.66,
      "end": 620.52,
      "text": "There's got to be some kind of experimental treatment or testing."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.9,
      "end": 621.18,
      "text": "There's not."
    },
    {
      "start": 621.26,
      "end": 621.68,
      "text": "I've looked."
    },
    {
      "start": 621.76,
      "end": 622.28,
      "text": "There's nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 622.38,
      "end": 625.2,
      "text": "There's nothing that wouldn't just prolong it or make it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 625.62,
      "end": 627.16,
      "text": "And I don't want you to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.24,
      "end": 628.8,
      "text": "And I don't want them to see me that way."
    },
    {
      "start": 629.22,
      "end": 630.22,
      "text": "So you just want me to do nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.62,
      "end": 631.52,
      "text": "We don't get to choose."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.04,
      "end": 632.3,
      "text": "Let me go."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.3,
      "end": 635.53,
      "text": "음 과연 what will happen next."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.93,
      "end": 636.49,
      "text": "궁금하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 636.75,
      "end": 637.15,
      "text": "I wonder."
    },
    {
      "start": 637.59,
      "end": 637.87,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.07,
      "end": 640.17,
      "text": "근데 there's only one day left."
    },
    {
      "start": 640.75,
      "end": 643.49,
      "text": "Oh we have one day to talk about this movie left."
    },
    {
      "start": 643.49,
      "end": 645.69,
      "text": "아 저는 약간 슬프게 이야기했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.69,
      "end": 649.71,
      "text": "우리 크리스쌤은 되게 밝게 이야기를 하셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 649.83,
      "end": 651.15,
      "text": "어 그래도 하루가 더 있네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 651.31,
      "end": 652.51,
      "text": "라는 느낌이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 652.95,
      "end": 653.65,
      "text": "You know what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.69,
      "end": 653.97,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.35,
      "end": 656.41,
      "text": "I don't want to talk a lot about disease."
    },
    {
      "start": 656.55,
      "end": 658.45,
      "text": "I've experienced that in my own family."
    },
    {
      "start": 658.59,
      "end": 660.67,
      "text": "I want to go to the next movie now."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.89,
      "end": 661.45,
      "text": "I'm ready."
    },
    {
      "start": 661.45,
      "end": 664.35,
      "text": "벌써 새로운 무비를 기대하고 계시네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 664.79,
      "end": 666.45,
      "text": "자 아무튼 오늘은 여기까지고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 666.61,
      "end": 668.43,
      "text": "우리는 내일 다시 만나도록 하겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 668.67,
      "end": 669.07,
      "text": "See you tomorrow."
    }
  ]
}